      <title>韩国强烈谴责金正恩投放垃圾气球等挑衅行为</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/south-korea-slams-kim-s-provocations-including-trash-balloons</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国总统尹锡烈表示，朝鲜向边境地区运送垃圾的气球应该感到羞耻，并加大了对金正恩政权的压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/south-korea-slams-kim-s-provocations-including-trash-balloons</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 03:01:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
