      <title>特朗普仅用一个视频在TikTok上迅速超越拜登</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-05/trump-quickly-surpasses-biden-in-tiktok-followers-and-likes-with-just-one-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[前总统唐纳德·特朗普于周六在 TikTok 上发布了他的第一个视频，该视频的关注者和点赞数已超过总统乔·拜登的竞选账号，两人在 11 月大选之前争夺关注度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-05/trump-quickly-surpasses-biden-in-tiktok-followers-and-likes-with-just-one-video</guid>
